
<h1><%=_('Product Assessment').html_safe%>
<br/><span class="tool_subtitle"><%=_('Introduction').html_safe%></span>
</h1>


<div class="content_skin">
   <%=_('The objective of this module is to assess the environmental performance of electronic products, considering their entire life-cycle.').html_safe%>
   <br/><br/>
   <%=_('In the <b>"DATA ENTRY"</b> module, you should enter the needed data for simulating your product (i.e. scenario, manufacturing, distribution, etc.), considering the different life-cycle steps.').html_safe%>
   <br/><br/>
   <ul>
     <li><%=_('<b>SCENARIO</b>.- Here you should introduce the lifetime of the product considering no technical failures occur, as well as, the annual device failure rate. In addition, the justification for the lifetime assumption must be added.').html_safe%></li>
     <li><%=_('<b>MANUFACTURING</b>.- Here you should introduce information associated to the components (material, quantity and age) that form the final product.').html_safe%></li>
     <li><%=_('<b>DISTRIBUTION</b>.- Here you should include information related to the packaging and transport needed to deliver the product from your manufacturing plant to your customer.').html_safe%></li>
     <li><%=_('<b>USE</b>.- Here you should include information related to the power consumption during the complete usage of your product. It includes also components replacement and transport to the repair shop.').html_safe%></li>
     <li><%=_('<b>END-OF-LIFE</b>.- Here you should include information about the components end-of-life scenario, i.e. recycling percentage of each of the components, as well as, reuse percentage from your device components at the end-of-life for other devices.').html_safe%></li>
   </ul>  
   <%=_('In order to present the results, you should select which Key Environmental Performance Indicators (KEPIs) you want to analyse.').html_safe%>
   <br/><br/>
   <%=_('In the <b>"RESULT"</b> module you could see the results using different perspectives:').html_safe%>
   <br/><br/>
   <ul>
	 <li><%=_('<b>"DETAILED RESULTS"</b> allow you to analyse in detail and numerically the quantity of materials previously selected in the KEPIs, as well as, the carbon footprint of the different stages.').html_safe%></li>
	 <li><%=_('<b>"GRAPHIC RESULTS"</b> show you in graphs the previous detailed results.').html_safe%></li>	 
	 <li><%=_('<b>"COMPARE RESULTS"</b> allow you to compare the results with other products already assessed, selecting beforehand the required indicators and LCA items to analyse.').html_safe%></li>
	 <li><%=_('<b>"SUMMARY RESULTS"</b> show the previous results in summarised graphics.').html_safe%></li>   
   </ul>   
